;B[ps]LB[qq:1][pq:2][rp:3][ps:4]C[Dia.1 Alive with two eyes

White's throw in at 1 looks like a sharp move but when it gets captured there is no way to capture Black.  Up to Black 4, he lives with two eyes.  If this were an endgame problem this would be fine, but it's not.
