;W[qq]LB[ps:1][pr:2][qq:3]C[Dia.3 Correct / Throw in

First you have to play the placement attack at 1 to get Black to connect at 2, then throw in at 3.  This was an easy problem right?  This might be difficult to find in a real game, so don't sweat it if you didn't find the answer immediately.
